Required Libraries:

Run the following command to install the required libraries:


Debian:
#sudo apt-get update 
#sudo apt-get install -y git nano python2 make gcc autoconf libtool python2-dev libpcre3-dev clamav
#sudo freshclam



RedHat, Fedora:
#sudo yum install -y nano python2 make gcc automake libtool python2-dev libpcre3-dev clamav
#sudo freshclam


